# TONG STUDIO - Font Consistency

## Font system (defined in index.css)
- **font-serif** (Cormorant Garamond): Section titles, main headings, card/article titles
- **font-sans** (Montserrat): Taglines, subsections, body text, labels, descriptions, buttons

## Usage
- Use `font-serif` for: h1, h2, section headings, card titles, logo, CTA headlines
- Use `font-sans` for: taglines ("You've seen our studios everywhere"), body paragraphs, labels (uppercase tracking), descriptions, nav links
